data.description: When you open the door to this adorable place, you'll know you're "HOME".  You will walk into the open floor-plan, that offers a generous living area with laminate flooring looking into the breakfast nook and kitchen.  Door in the kitchen leads to covered back porch and large fenced yard with an extra concrete pad for grilling and entertaining.  The master bedroom has laminate flooring and a large closet while the master bathroom, boasts double sinks and a stand up shower.  Palm Gardens is a small community in the Fernandina school district that is easy access to Amelia Concourse and Yulee shopping as well as Amelia Island beaches, historic Fernandina Beach and our quaint downtown area. This well priced home won't last long!
